creme::::.github/workflows/dev-docs.yml::::jobs::::ubuntu::::steps::::steps_6::::run::::git config user.name github-actions
git config user.email github-actions@github.com
git config pull.rebase false

git add --all
git commit -m "Release dev docs" --allow-empty

git fetch
git checkout gh-pages
git pull

git checkout main
mike deploy dev --push --remote https://github.com/online-ml/river.git

creme::::.github/workflows/release-docs.yml::::jobs::::ubuntu::::steps::::steps_3::::run::::python -m pip install --upgrade pip
pip install wheel
pip install -e ".[compat,docs]"
pip install git+https://github.com/MaxHalford/yamp
python -m spacy download en_core_web_sm

creme::::.github/workflows/release-docs.yml::::jobs::::ubuntu::::steps::::steps_6::::run::::git config user.name github-actions
git config user.email github-actions@github.com
git config pull.rebase false

git add --all
git commit -m "Execute notebooks"

git fetch
git checkout gh-pages
git pull

git checkout main
RIVER_VERSION=$(python -c "import river; print(river.__version__)")
mike deploy ${RIVER_VERSION} latest --update-aliases --push --force --remote https://${GH_TOKEN}@github.com/online-ml/river.git
